  "description": {
    "zh": "最后的测试任务。\n\n我们需要测试一种特定配置的 M60 机枪，能搞定吗？它必须装上 458mm 短管以及一款 Aimpoint 的红点瞄具。\n\n带着这把枪去TerraGroup集团实验室，给我清理一下那片地方。任务完成后你会拿到报酬。记得尽快回来，咱俩说好了的。",
    "en": "Your last test.\n\nWe need these M60 machineguns tested in a specific configuration, can you do that? It needs to have a short barrel and a reflex sight made by aimpoint.\n\nYou need to take this weapon to the Terragroup laboratory and clean up that place a little. You'll receive your payment after the job is done. Promise that I will hear from you soon?"
  },
